│                                                              │
│ The root cause lies in `ScalarEvolution::getMulExpr`. When   │
│ creating a SCEV expression for a `mul` instruction with an   │
│ `nsw` flag, SCEV does not properly account for the `nsw`     │
│ semantics when one of the operands is a constant.            │
